Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却平静地说出这些话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 真见外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也曾是00的成员 不管何时 成员都团结一心 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心情 现在也和翼一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要赶不上电车了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 麻里子是袭名成员 有专车接送吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也乘电车回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻里子 这样可不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:04:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袭名成员对研究生异常地用心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和袭名成员还是研究生无关
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要按照我的想法去做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有女王气质嘛 麻里子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我兴奋不已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好坏好坏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美森麻里 也欺负欺负楚方嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欺负楚方嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs30}好了 楚方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是优子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.74,0:04:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边 涡轮哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是有谁在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楚方的视力太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那种地方 做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:04:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌声果然很美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来的确是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这么大噪音的涡轮旁边竟然也能听见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但确实是优子的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子在传达她的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使总选举取得第一 她也没有满足
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像要追求比现在更高的目标的呐喊一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帅过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子的照片都收起来是不是太浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是再贴出来比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有优子的新生写哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你有真琴的生写的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是可以便宜换给你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:06:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃——子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,STOP
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kojiharu动作慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻里子要注意周围的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往Tomochin的位置过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛岛老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事 优子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让我们自己稍微练习一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 我的练习强度不够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 强度严重不够
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 我告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,练习中突然逃走的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不知道什么时候按快门才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我知道她确实是才华横溢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的优子姐 虽然平时看似跟以前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是偶尔会像刚才那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很难搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 总觉得有些…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉就像圣人一般
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也见过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟大家一起欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被大家所爱戴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却总觉得很难接近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算处在大家之中也会觉得她高不可攀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是说啊酱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,13代啊酱也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为Center Nova之后的一段时间里 一直都是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪都不太接近他人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散发出让人无法随意搭话的气场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊酱你…好像渐渐地变得形单影只了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形单影只? 为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道 但是总有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 大家都是喜欢啊酱的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以可以更依赖大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的啊酱 总感觉一直在一个人战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也最喜欢各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你为我担心了 麻里子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊酱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的 我不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我的孤独到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊酱在那之后就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失的Center Nova们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们到底消失到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果还能再见面的话 那到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火热的太阳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻人的肌肤果然就是不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水嫩透白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:10:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咪酱 好歹披个毛巾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,663)}孤独はいつでも　自由のお代偿に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论何时孤独都是 获取自由的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 优子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就算付出巨大的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也希望前往那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会被任何人所妨碍之地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神圣的Position 0
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Position 0…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋叶星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该星球地表下蕴藏有丰富的双晶素
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 还有能激活双晶素
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使Kirara强烈闪耀的太阳之女神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要感谢上苍啊 甚至让我想跳过即将要发生的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.73,0:11:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子姐好闪耀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像真的习惯了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子姐的话 一定可以成为Center Nova的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 成为Center Nova的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总选举时 优子姐不是说过不会消失的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子姐的话 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Center Nova发生条件之一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在秋叶星举办Live
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要成为Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须能承受孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤独?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 闪耀强大光芒的背后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要伴随着更深的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被嫉妒 被敌视
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至被利用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Position 0就是背负这一切情感的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果能战胜黑暗保持自我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就能站上梦寐已久之处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空无一人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候 眼前的位置一直属于啊酱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许正是她的身躯保护了我 让我不被狂风卷走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后如今
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的眼前空无一人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然间怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急事态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请秋叶星居民尽快到掩体处避难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避难?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DES军的大部队越过了启动中的防卫线 向这里逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,研究生她们已经出动了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,产生Center Nova的第二个条件是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气反常的演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气象控制系统也许被黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楚方的秋叶星才不会是这样电闪雷鸣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位上 为了守卫秋叶星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,织音 快脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友歌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 让人着实捏了把汗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和承诺不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承诺?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼 这样下去会危及到神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.93,0:15:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DES 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Zodiac的目标是双晶素和Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Zodiac?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kojiharu Tomochin
